data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house located in the desirable city of Jacksonville, FL. This lovely home offers a range of amenities that are sure to enhance your living experience. Step inside to discover a spacious open space kitchen, perfect for preparing delicious meals and entertaining guests. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the dining zone, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The house also features a fully fenced backyard, providing a private space for outdoor activities. Enjoy the convenience of having a washer and dryer in the comfort of your own home, making laundry day a breeze. Additionally, this house offers a carport, with additional parking in the driveway. Imagine cozy evenings spent around the fire pit, creating lasting memories with loved ones. The stainless appliances add a touch of elegance to the kitchen, making cooking a pleasure. Step outside onto the back patio and soak up the Florida sunshine while enjoying a cup of coffee or simply unwinding after a long day. With its prime location and array of amenities, this house is the perfect place to call home. 

Resident benefit package is required. Includes move-in concierge services, online portal access, document storage, multiple payment options, credit reporting and liability and personal property insurance. Monthly cost - $50.00 per month. Lease preparation fee - $125.00.
Pet friendly too! Approved pet okay with pet screening, monthly fee and $125 initial pet admin fee.

Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to live in a beautiful house in Jacksonville, FL. Contact us today and experience the charm of this wonderful home for yourself.
